ana intensive(expensive), so that we may create a nice bit of burst damage for a short period, before going OOM.  This would truly link a ranger to his mana, which is not the case at present.<br /><br />My 2cp.<br /><br /></p><br /><span class="sm">----------------------------</span><br /><i>"It is idiotic to quote a bunch of nobodies in your signature." - Reinman</i><br /><br /><a href="HTTP://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=596992" target="akztarg">Reinmon</a>, <span class="sm">58 Ranger</span><br /> <a href="HTTP://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=758729" target="akztarg">Slaher</a>, <span class="sm">58 Shaman</span><br /><a href="HTTP://www.guildportal.com/Guild.aspx?GuildID=15391&TabID=129880 " target="akztarg">Aude Sapere</a><br />Povar Server "Resistance is Futile." </td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td id="fs8">Posting from your fantasies.</td></tr></table>
